    "roasterUrl": "https://kmen.coffee",
    "coffeeUrl": "https://kmen.coffee/kava/espresso/",
    "coffeeDescription": "Kmen Coffee Roasters — Ethiopia Iron Lion. Named after the Bob Marley song Iron Lion Zion. Natural process, espresso roast. Flavor: plums, lemon sorbet, green tea. 250g. Roasted in Ceske Budejovice. Roasted 10.12.2025.",
    "notes": "Home espresso, Sculptor 064S. Dialed over 2 days. Started at 4.0 (choked), worked up to 6.5 (too fast), bracketed between 5.8 (bitter) and 5.9/40g (sweet spot). Final: grind 5.9, 18g/40g (1:2.22), 28s, 92C. Flavor: tea and citrus opening, plum body, clean finish — no bitterness. 40g yield key — 36g too bitter, 41.6g too flat. Works well with milk. My Pick."
  },
